name: Metafox
description: For 9 years, the MetaMask Fox has been the silent guardian of Ethereum - watching over billions in assets, guiding users through the wilds of Web3, and standing as the most iconic face in crypto. But now… he’s breaking out of the wallet. No longer content being just a tool, MetaFox is stepping into the meme arena - not as a trend follower, but as the symbol of trust, freedom, and crypto rebellion. There was never supposed to be a token. Until now. Connect wallet. You may already qualify.
